&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the VP of Strategic Partnerships, you will be the driving force behind aligning Couchbase Capella with the cloud ecosystems to accelerate co-sell motions, maximize cloud marketplace adoption, and achieve mutual ARR growth.&lt;/p&gt;
