&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive GTM Strategy Across All Three Clouds:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the primary contact and operational point of contact for AWS, Microsoft Azure, and GCP. Develop and execute a comprehensive global alliance business plan for each provider designed to accelerate Couchbase Capella adoption and grow consumption on their clouds.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Executive Partner Relationships:&lt;/strong&gt; Build out executive relationships within each provider’s partner organization — spanning co-sell, partner programs, and marketplace teams — to secure sponsorship, funding, and preferred-partner positioning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Co-Innovation &amp;amp; Integrations:&lt;/strong&gt; Build relationships with and lead efforts on product innovation and integrations alongside each provider’s product and engineering teams, positioning Couchbase Capella data platform and AI Data plane on every cloud.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sales &amp;amp; Marketing Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Build relationships across each provider’s sales and marketing organizations to expand co-sell and collaboration in the field, applying an industry lens to joint account targeting and vertical GTM plays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
